msgctxt "mn151:19.6"
msgid "‘bhāvitā kho me samatho ca vipassanā cā’ti, tena, sāriputta, bhikkhunā teneva pītipāmojjena vihātabbaṃ ahorattānusikkhinā kusalesu dhammesu. "
msgstr "they have developed them, they should meditate with rapture and joy, training day and night in skillful qualities. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya20, sc15
msgctxt "mn151:20.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, sāriputta, bhikkhunā iti paṭisañcikkhitabbaṃ: "
msgstr "Furthermore, a mendicant should reflect: "

msgctxt "mn151:20.2"
msgid "‘sacchikatā nu kho me vijjā ca vimutti cā’ti? "
msgstr "‘Have I realized knowledge and freedom?’ "

msgctxt "mn151:20.3"
msgid "Sace, sāriputta, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti: "
msgstr "Suppose that, upon checking, a mendicant knows that "

msgctxt "mn151:20.4"
msgid "‘asacchikatā kho me vijjā ca vimutti cā’ti, tena, sāriputta, bhikkhunā vijjāya vimuttiyā sacchikiriyāya vāyamitabbaṃ. "
msgstr "they haven’t realized them, they should make an effort to do so. "

msgctxt "mn151:20.5"
msgid "Sace pana, sāriputta, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti: "
msgstr "But suppose that, upon checking, a mendicant knows that "

msgctxt "mn151:20.6"
msgid "‘sacchikatā kho me vijjā ca vimutti cā’ti, tena, sāriputta, bhikkhunā teneva pītipāmojjena vihātabbaṃ ahorattānusikkhinā kusalesu dhammesu. "
msgstr "they have realized them, they should meditate with rapture and joy, training day and night in skillful qualities. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya21, sc16
msgctxt "mn151:21.1"
msgid "Ye hi keci, sāriputta, atītamaddhānaṃ samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā piṇḍapātaṃ parisodhesuṃ, sabbe te evameva paccavekkhitvā paccavekkhitvā piṇḍapātaṃ parisodhesuṃ. "
msgstr "Whether in the past, future, or present, all those who purify their alms-food do so by continually checking in this way. "

msgctxt "mn151:21.2"
msgid "Yepi hi keci, sāriputta, anāgatamaddhānaṃ samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā piṇḍapātaṃ parisodhessanti, sabbe te evameva paccavekkhitvā paccavekkhitvā piṇḍapātaṃ parisodhessanti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn151:21.3"
msgid "Yepi hi keci, sāriputta, etarahi samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā piṇḍapātaṃ parisodhenti, sabbe te evameva paccavekkhitvā paccavekkhitvā piṇḍapātaṃ parisodhenti. "
msgstr " "

#. VAR: Tasmātiha, sāriputta → tena hi vo sāriputta evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ (bj, pts1) | tasmātiha vo sāriputta sikkhitabbaṃ (s1, s2) | tasmātiha vo sārīputta sikkhitabbaṃ (s3)
msgctxt "mn151:21.4"
msgid "Tasmātiha, sāriputta, ‘paccavekkhitvā paccavekkhitvā piṇḍapātaṃ parisodhessāmā’ti—"
msgstr "So, Sāriputta, you should all train like this: ‘We shall purify our alms-food by continually checking.’” "

msgctxt "mn151:21.5"
msgid "evañhi vo, sāriputta, sikkhitabban”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc17
msgctxt "mn151:21.6"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā. "
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said. "

msgctxt "mn151:21.7"
msgid "Attamano āyasmā sāriputto bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinandīti. "
msgstr "Satisfied, Venerable Sāriputta was happy with what the Buddha said. "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "mn151:21.8"
msgid "Piṇḍapātapārisuddhisuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ navamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

